1) License for Atmel-derived MCU-code

Most of the firmware code in the "usb_device" subdirectory is adapted from the
Microchip/Atmel application note AVR273 on how to implement a USB Mass Storage
Device on ATmega devices; the original code can be downloaded here:
http://www.atmel.com/Images/AVR273_USB_Mass_Storage.zip

Correspondingly, all source files retaining the below copyright notice by
Atmel are subject to its rules and restrictions.


